OL,3,CDouble murder accused killed cellmate
OL,4,Cwhile awaiting trial, court told
OL,6,FA man who is accused of murdering two
OL,7,Fmen whose remains were discovered in
OL,8,Fremote woodland in Cornwall has
OL,9,Falready been convicted of the murder
OL,10,Fof his prison cellmate, a jury has
OL,11,Fbeen told.
OL,13,FJames Desborough, 40, strangled his
OL,14,Fcellmate Steven Kempster at HMP Exeter
OL,15,Fon 15 September last year.
OL,17,FJurors at Winchester Crown Court heard
OL,18,Fon Monday (20 July) that Desborough
OL,19,Fwas on remand at the time over the
OL,20,Fcurrent allegations he faces.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
