CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784659707
OL,3,CDouble murder accused killed cellmate
OL,4,Cwhile awaiting trial, court told
OL,6,FHe has pleaded guilty to failing to
OL,7,Fallow the lawful burial of the two
OL,8,Fmen's bodies.
OL,10,FThe trial continues.
